Class CaseExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.CaseExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression

    public class CaseExpression
extends java.lang.Object
implements Expression
    CASE/WHEN expression. Syntax: CASE WHEN condition THEN expression [WHEN condition THEN expression]... [ELSE expression] END or CASE expression WHEN condition THEN expression [WHEN condition THEN expression]... [ELSE expression] END See also: https://aurora.vcu.edu/db2help/db2s0/frame3.htm#casexp http://sybooks.sybase.com/onlinebooks/group-as/asg1251e/commands/@ebt-link;pt=5954?target=%25N%15_52628_START_RESTART_N%25
    Author:
    Havard Rast Blok
